</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>vehicle</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='email' href='#email'></a> email</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Email address configured in Torque application.</p>
</span></p></dd></dl>
</div>
